          s4title: "④ Reaching 1.0",
          s4body: `On <b>2026-06-25</b>, the <code>.krs</code> / <code>.krs.style</code> language spec was finalized as <strong style="color:var(--refactor)">v1.0 (stable)</strong> (#1780). Starting from the core idea of separating logical and physical structure, karasu built up two-layer rendering, multi-file imports, the client kind, a layout engine, a Chat UI, a suite of CLI tools, a diagnostics catalog, a documentation site, and OSS publishing infrastructure over roughly <b>15</b> weeks — leaving behind 237 design decisions (ADRs) and 64 test perspectives (TPLs) as knowledge assets.`,
          foot: "This report is auto-extracted from the karasu repository's git history, <code>docs/adr/</code>, and <code>docs/test-perspectives/</code>.<br>Snapshot: 2026-06-25 · single self-contained HTML file (no external dependencies).",
