                "ADR-20260428-06: Introduce the client kind",
                "feat(core): client kind — Phases 1–7 (#861–#896)",
                "feat(cli): karasu diff / translate / apply",
                "feat(app): ship the diff viewer by default (#840)",
              ],
            },
            {
              name: "May",
              subtitle: "Consolidation — TPLs begin and the UI is refreshed",
              narrative:
                "A month of quality and regression prevention. <strong>ADR-20260509-04 started the Test Perspective Library (TPL) practice</strong> — 23 perspectives in the first week alone, 40 by month's end. The Tidy Style formatter and value-level <code>.krs.style</code> diagnostics were completed. The UI migrated to <strong>shadcn/ui + Tailwind v4</strong>, adding a command palette, keyboard shortcuts, an AST Outline view, and light/dark themes. <code>reference-data.ts</code> became the single source of truth for spec tables, changesets automated releases, and tpl-tools / the hane plugin were extracted into external packages. May 23 – Jun 10 was a pause.",
              highlights: [
                "ADR-20260509-04: Start the Test Perspective Library (TPL)",
